No. 13,796. Estate of Solis. Young, Administratrix, et al. v. Solis.

( ... P. [2d] ... )

Decided May 25, 1936.

Judgment affirmed in department without written opinion, Mr. Justice Burke, sitting for Mr. Chief Justice Campbell, Mr. Justice Butler and Mr. Justice Holland participating.

*554Mr. Joseph J. Walsh, Mr. Donald F. Clifford, for plaintiffs in error. Messrs. Bartels, Blood & Bancroft, for defendants in error.
